  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game requires Xbox gamepads for local multiplayer</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>INTENSE SHOWDOWN AT THE TAVERN IN LOCAL MULTIPLAYER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Which squire will best defend their knight's honor? Challenge up to 4 friends in epic  and intense matches to decide! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/baf43e62cc60377f8ddd4221abaf23a6.poster.avif?t=1751560030\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/baf43e62cc60377f8ddd4221abaf23a6.webm?t=1751560030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/baf43e62cc60377f8ddd4221abaf23a6.mp4?t=1751560030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WIELD YOUR SWORD WITH DEXTERITY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your sword is your most precious resource. Learn to parry attacks, disarm your opponents or hit the bull's-eye with an arena-crossing throw. Watch out for bounces, though, and make sure you don't find yourself cornered and unarmed. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/054a6eb44cda6199b552990536cdc83a.poster.avif?t=1751560030\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/054a6eb44cda6199b552990536cdc83a.webm?t=1751560030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/054a6eb44cda6199b552990536cdc83a.mp4?t=1751560030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ACCOMPLISH THE CROWD'S QUEST</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn as many points as possible by completing the quests given by the public in each round. Be clever and vary your strategies to surprise your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/2a46a04618d43e23d21022340bee9d57.poster.avif?t=1751560030\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/2a46a04618d43e23d21022340bee9d57.webm?t=1751560030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/2a46a04618d43e23d21022340bee9d57.mp4?t=1751560030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KBF can be played with a keyboard, but we recommend using a controller. The game is compatible with Xbox controllers.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game requires Xbox gamepads for local multiplayer</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>INTENSE SHOWDOWN AT THE TAVERN IN LOCAL MULTIPLAYER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Which squire will best defend their knight's honor? Challenge up to 4 friends in epic  and intense matches to decide! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/baf43e62cc60377f8ddd4221abaf23a6.poster.avif?t=1751560030\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/baf43e62cc60377f8ddd4221abaf23a6.webm?t=1751560030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/baf43e62cc60377f8ddd4221abaf23a6.mp4?t=1751560030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WIELD YOUR SWORD WITH DEXTERITY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your sword is your most precious resource. Learn to parry attacks, disarm your opponents or hit the bull's-eye with an arena-crossing throw. Watch out for bounces, though, and make sure you don't find yourself cornered and unarmed. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/054a6eb44cda6199b552990536cdc83a.poster.avif?t=1751560030\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/054a6eb44cda6199b552990536cdc83a.webm?t=1751560030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/054a6eb44cda6199b552990536cdc83a.mp4?t=1751560030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ACCOMPLISH THE CROWD'S QUEST</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn as many points as possible by completing the quests given by the public in each round. Be clever and vary your strategies to surprise your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/2a46a04618d43e23d21022340bee9d57.poster.avif?t=1751560030\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/2a46a04618d43e23d21022340bee9d57.webm?t=1751560030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738440/extras/2a46a04618d43e23d21022340bee9d57.mp4?t=1751560030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KBF can be played with a keyboard, but we recommend using a controller. The game is compatible with Xbox controllers.</p>",
